			<![CDATA[<b>A:</b>	&nbsp;<blank word="Have you eaten dinner yet?"/> 
<b>B:</b>	No, I haven't.  Let’s go out.
<b>A:</b>	&nbsp;<blank word="Have you been to the new Hungarian restaurant?"/>  
<b>B:</b>	No, I've never been there.  I’ve heard it's very good.
<b>A:</b>	&nbsp;<blank word="Let's go.  They have excellent goulash."/> 
<b>B:</b>	You know, I’ve never tried goulash. 
<b>A:</b>	&nbsp;<blank word="I think you’ll like it. It's delicious!"/>]]>
